# Component Map — Matching Refined Blueprint and Wireframe

## Purpose
Translate the approved blueprint and wireframe into a build-ready component architecture.

This map defines:
- component hierarchy
- responsibilities per component
- props contracts
- placeholder data model for current proof blocks

---

