## Page Assembly Contract

In app/page.tsx, compose sections in this exact order:
1. HeroSection
2. ExpertiseSection
3. ProofBlockSection (proofBlocks[0])
4. ProofBlockSection (proofBlocks[1])
5. PhilosophySection
6. ContactSection

Shared wrappers:
- SiteShell wraps the full page
- StickyHeader appears above main
- SiteFooter appears after main content

