## Implementation Notes

- Keep accent token fixed to #A3E635 in theme variables.
- Keep proof block media containers fixed-ratio to prevent layout shift when real images replace placeholders.
- Maintain text-first ordering on mobile for both proof blocks regardless of desktop alternation.
- Respect reduced-motion preferences in all animated components.
